Subject: RE: [archive-crawler] wayback gzip support





Hi, 



All versions only support GZIP WARCs, AFAICT. However, there are problems
parsing some WARCs produced be some versions of wget (see
https://github.com/ukwa/warc-explorer/issues/5#issuecomment-18432671) -
using version 1.7.1 appears to be more reliable.



What versions have you tried? What errors did you see? Can you provide test
data that reproduces the problem?



Thanks,

Andy



